  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/d9f955d3c6ee476ec46898f93ca46af1.avif?t=1773329059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras_big/d9f955d3c6ee476ec46898f93ca46af1.avif?t=1773329059 width=1560 height=822 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>Updated as of March 9th, 2026</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The Game Formally Known As 'Get To The Orange Door' was in development for eight and a half years...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It received many updates over that time, evolving into a much larger and more ambitious project. Eighteen months ago, we set out to fully capture the core essence of ALL the past versions  into one, final game. With the support of our community, we have been working tirelessly to accomplish this task. While we're not ready to unveil everything yet, we wanted to be perfectly clear with anyone reading our Steam page as to the current state of GTTOD:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/1555948258151336b18ee59aff8e5789.avif?t=1773329059\" width=663 height=259 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The screenshots, trailers, and promotional images below represent what is currently available on Steam; NOT what will be available in upcoming playtests, betas, or the full release of GTTOD. If you have any questions regarding update progress, regular updates are posted here on Steam and in the Discord server. <br> <br>Below is the unedited store page for '<i>Get To The Orange Door':</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/9c8338905e234954955c40d471341d48.avif?t=1773329059\" width=613 height=85 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/a2f9ed308272ba60dd1575fad84ca412.poster.avif?t=1773329059\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/a2f9ed308272ba60dd1575fad84ca412.webm?t=1773329059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/a2f9ed308272ba60dd1575fad84ca412.mp4?t=1773329059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GTTOD is a fast paced FPS rogue-like with a heavy focus on fluidity of movement and high octane combat. Casting its net of inspirations wide, GTTOD captures both the feel of modern day movement shooters as well as the chaotic intensity of the best FPS games in the '90s. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/5bb1537ed039bc13c590d2566aa58f75.poster.avif?t=1773329059\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/5bb1537ed039bc13c590d2566aa58f75.webm?t=1773329059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/5bb1537ed039bc13c590d2566aa58f75.mp4?t=1773329059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXTINGUISH THE HORDES OF THE SUMMIT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As one of the power-armor clad survivors in The Shatter, you'll be using your advanced mobility and a myriad of reclaimed firearms and equipment to outmaneuver and outgun the armies of a planet-destroying threat; The World Sentinel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/f9bf5083a669edba653cfdde54132c36.poster.avif?t=1773329059\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/f9bf5083a669edba653cfdde54132c36.webm?t=1773329059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/f9bf5083a669edba653cfdde54132c36.mp4?t=1773329059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WIELD THE BLESSINGS OF THE WORLD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are not alone. As a child of Earth, you are able to inherit the abilities bestowed upon you by The Spirit Of The World, and use them to destroy those that threaten her safety.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/320752636eae56541178e5e3a43987e4.poster.avif?t=1773329059\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/320752636eae56541178e5e3a43987e4.webm?t=1773329059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/320752636eae56541178e5e3a43987e4.mp4?t=1773329059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNLEASH YOUR INNER POTENTIAL</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Permanently improve your skills and abilities, allowing you to endure the unending trials of The Shatter. Lengthen your treks into the unforgiving world, and reap the rewards of your conquest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/383d047615a09406073045d96919285b.poster.avif?t=1773329059\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/383d047615a09406073045d96919285b.webm?t=1773329059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/383d047615a09406073045d96919285b.mp4?t=1773329059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RISE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore, loot, and gear up for your ascension towards the upmost peak of The Shatter; \"The Summit\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/2b2bea3395393686fd309725bb3e6518.poster.avif?t=1773329059\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/2b2bea3395393686fd309725bb3e6518.webm?t=1773329059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/2b2bea3395393686fd309725bb3e6518.mp4?t=1773329059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REPEAT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Death is not the end. Each new run of GTTOD shifts destinations and routes on your journey to The Summit. No playthrough is ever the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/7731dfaa85f86bb07460c4598f592c8d.avif?t=1773329059\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>If you'd like to keep up with the game, feel free to join the Discord and chat with me!</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/d9f955d3c6ee476ec46898f93ca46af1.avif?t=1773329059\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras_big/d9f955d3c6ee476ec46898f93ca46af1.avif?t=1773329059 width=1560 height=822 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>Updated as of March 9th, 2026</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The Game Formally Known As 'Get To The Orange Door' was in development for eight and a half years...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It received many updates over that time, evolving into a much larger and more ambitious project. Eighteen months ago, we set out to fully capture the core essence of ALL the past versions  into one, final game. With the support of our community, we have been working tirelessly to accomplish this task. While we're not ready to unveil everything yet, we wanted to be perfectly clear with anyone reading our Steam page as to the current state of GTTOD:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/1555948258151336b18ee59aff8e5789.avif?t=1773329059\" width=663 height=259 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The screenshots, trailers, and promotional images below represent what is currently available on Steam; NOT what will be available in upcoming playtests, betas, or the full release of GTTOD. If you have any questions regarding update progress, regular updates are posted here on Steam and in the Discord server. <br> <br>Below is the unedited store page for '<i>Get To The Orange Door':</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/541200/extras/9c8338905e234